c: 33
v: 33
t: "Mujye munaguma mu ngo zanyu kandi ntimukagaragaze imitako yanyu nk’uko abagore bo mu bihe by’ubujiji babikoraga. Mujye muhozaho iswala, mutange amaturo kandi mwumvire Allah n’Intumwa ye. Mu by’ukuri yemwe bantu bo mu rugo (rw’Intumwa)! Allah arashaka kubakuriraho ibibi n’ibyaha ndetse no kubasukura byimazeyo"